graph TD
    A[User Inputs Text & Font] --> B[Service: Generate SVG Request]
    B --> C[svgGenerator Domain]
    C --> D[Load Font via opentype.js]
    D --> E[Get Glyph Path]
    E --> F{Is Outline Type?}
    F -- No --> G[Base Path Geometry]
    F -- Yes --> H[Generate Offset Path Geometry]
    H --> I[Convert Path to Polygon]
    I --> J[Apply ClipperOffset]
    J --> K[Convert back to SVG Path Data]
    G --> L[Construct SVG XML]
    K --> L
    L --> M[Return SVG to Client]
    M --> N[User Downloads & Imports to TinkerCad]
